         <div type="translation">
            <ab>MH 2631, recto: (1) Pasemis, son of Pamonthes, has paid to the bank (2) of the northern house (3) for the silver of poll of year 26, among the men of Harsiesis, son of (4) Khonstefnakhte, 2 staters / 1 stater / 2 staters again. Written in (5) year 26, Pachons 29.</ab>
